உண் டாகு. note; போடுadded to a transitive verb has an intensive force  
4. [ இடு 4.]  
pootu (poota  
poottu) போடு (போட  
போட்டு) put  
place (unintentionally or carelessly); throw (away)  
drop; give birth to (of animals); helping verb with numerous nouns with general idea of put: draw (a picture)  
put in (a road)  
